# See https://help.github.com/articles/ignoring-files/ for more about ignoring files.

# Ignore node_modules for all subdirectories
**/node_modules

# Ignore Yarn configuration (if you're using Yarn)
**/.pnp
**/.pnp.*
**/.yarn/*
!**/.yarn/patches
!**/.yarn/plugins
!**/.yarn/releases
!**/.yarn/versions

# Ignore testing directories and files
**/coverage

# Ignore Next.js build output
**/.next
**/out

# Ignore production build directories
**/build

# Miscellaneous system files
.DS_Store
*.pem

# Ignore log files generated by npm and Yarn
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*

# Ignore environment files (opt-in if necessary)
**/.env*

# Ignore Vercel configuration files (if used)
**/.vercel

# Ignore TypeScript build info files
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Ignore Next.js environment declaration file
next-env.d.ts
